Internal storage:

    -   always available.
    -   private
    -   files are removed when app is uninstalled
    -   best to be sure that neither the user nor other apps can access your files

External storage:

    -   not always available
    -   world-readable
    -   files are removed when app is uninstalled only if save them in the directory from getExternalFilesDir()
    -   best place for files that don't require access restrictions

    Public files :
        -   freely available to other apps and to the user
        -   remain available after uninstall

    Private files :
        -   don't provide value to the user outside the app
        -   deleted after uninstall
